    "These comment data contain rich user experiences, which are crucial for companies to understand user sentiments.",
    "Sentiment analysis of comment text is a hot research direction in text mining.",
    "Compared to sentence-level sentiment analysis, aspect-based sentiment analysis can provide more in-depth and finegrained information.",
